        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/magicelf1988/" class="name">Summer</a>

            <span class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>

        <span content="2008-03-10" class="main-meta">2008-03-10 21:50:01</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://movie.douban.com/review/1323266/">为你，千千万万次。</a></h2>

                <div id="review_1323266_short" class="review-short" data-rid="1323266">
                    <div class="short-content">
                            <p class="spoiler-tip">这篇影评可能有剧透</p>

                        if we come to sleep we are his drowsy ones and if we come to wake we are in his hands if we come to weeping we are his cloud full of raindrops and if we come to laughing we are his lightning in that moment if we come to anger and battle it is the reflection...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1323266-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
